quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  17,23,"Ndipo Ambuye wako walamula kuti musapembedze wina aliyense koma Iye yekha. Ndipo kuti muwachitire makolo anu zabwino. Ngati wina wa iwo kapena onse akalamba ali kukhala nanu, musawakalipire ayi, koma muziwayankhula ndi mawu aulemu"
  17,24,"Onetsani kudzichepetsa ndi chisoni ndipo munene kuti, “Ambuye wanga! Achitireni chifundo monga momwe iwo adandilerera pamene ine ndidali wamng’ono.”"
  17,25,Ambuye wanu amadziwa kwambiri zonse zimene zili m’mitima mwanu. Ngati muli abwino ndithudi Iye ali wokhululukira kwa anthu amene amadza kwa Iye nthawi zonse modzichepetsa ndi kulapa
  17,26,Ndipo apatseni abale anu ndi anthu ovutika gawo lawo lowayenera ndiponso a paulendo amene avutika. Ndipo musapereke chuma chanu moononga
  17,27,"Ndithudi anthu oononga ndi abale a Satana ndipo Satana, kwa Ambuye wake, ndi wosayamika"
  17,28,"Ndipo ngati iwe siuwathandiza ndipo uli kuyembekezera chisomo chochokera kwa Ambuye wako, yankhula nawo mwachifundo ndi mawu oleza"
  17,29,Ndipo musakhale oumira kapena opereka moononga chifukwa mungadzudzulidwe kapena kukhala osauka kwambiri
  17,30,"Ndithudi Ambuye wako amapereka zambiri kwa aliyense amene wamufuna ndipo amanyalapsa. Ndithudi Iye, kwa akapolo ake, ndi wodziwa ndi woona"